{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji19.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给李富春的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给李富春的信！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年3月29日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中共七大政治报告修改本今日印五十本，留一本给我，四十九本由秦邦宪交你。今日给参加七中全会的每人发一本，叫他们收到即看，附白纸一张，请他们再写意见，于三十一日开会时带交。给陈绍禹、冈野进、王稼祥各发一本。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致李富春信的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1945,"month":3,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":362,"page_end":362},"tags":[{"name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}